            <title>The Front Desk</title>
            <link>http://localhost:1313/guestbook/</link>
            <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
            <guid>http://localhost:1313/guestbook/</guid>
            <description>&lt;p&gt;Welcome to Field Notes.&#xA;Whether we&amp;rsquo;ve known each other for years or you&amp;rsquo;ve only just wandered in, I&amp;rsquo;m glad you&amp;rsquo;re here.&#xA;If you&amp;rsquo;d like to say hello, ask a question, request a library card, join the Frame, or simply tell me what brought you here, this is the place to do it.&#xA;I read every note.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;library-card&#34;&gt;Library Card&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Browse my private book collection.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;If you&amp;rsquo;d like access to my personal library, leave me a note below.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://library.spyke.space/&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&#xA;    &gt;→ Enter the Library&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;the-frame&#34;&gt;The Frame&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Show me what you see.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;http://localhost:1313/blog/the-frame/&#34; &gt;→ Learn about the Frame&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;say-hi&#34;&gt;Say hi&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Leave a note, ask a question, or tell me what brought you here.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;A free GitHub account is required to sign the guestbook.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;script src=&#34;https://giscus.app/client.js&#34;&#xA;        data-repo=&#34;awesomespyke/field-notes&#34;&#xA;        data-repo-id=&#34;R_kgDOSuaJxA&#34;&#xA;        data-category=&#34;General&#34;&#xA;        data-category-id=&#34;DIC_kwDOSuaJxM4C_KSA&#34;&#xA;        data-mapping=&#34;pathname&#34;&#xA;        data-strict=&#34;0&#34;&#xA;        data-reactions-enabled=&#34;0&#34;&#xA;        data-emit-metadata=&#34;0&#34;&#xA;        data-input-position=&#34;top&#34;&#xA;        data-theme=&#34;preferred_color_scheme&#34;&#xA;        data-lang=&#34;en&#34;&#xA;        crossorigin=&#34;anonymous&#34;&#xA;        async&gt;&#xA;&lt;/script&gt;<